    <text id="A6184T">
        <front id="d2">
            <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
                <p>Evans writes his wife, Mary Anna Sibert, that her father's illness has delayed
                    their return home.</p>
            </div1>
        </front>

        <body id="d4">
            <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        <date value="1870-01-22">Jan 22 1870</date>
                        <name type="place">Gordonsville</name>
                    </dateline>
                    <salute>My Dear Wife</salute>
                </opener>

                <p>I wrote you on Yesterday that we would be home <orig reg="today">to day</orig>
                    your Pa was taken Sick in Washington on last Wednesday night with the Cramp
                    Colick we came as far as this place we had to lay over your Pa was too Sick to
                    travel further. he is better this Morning. I Sent a Telegram to John A Noon last
                    Night to take out just as Soon as he <abbr expan="received">Recd</abbr> it. I
                        <abbr expan="received">Recd</abbr> one from him This Morning &amp; from
                    the tone of his Telegram I <orig reg="don't">dont</orig> think he Sent My out
                    last night I <orig reg="wanted">wantted</orig> Ma to get it in time to Come down
                    on the train this Morning, for it May be <orig reg="several">Severl</orig> Days
                        <orig reg="before">be fore</orig> your Pa will be <orig reg="able"
                    >abel</orig> to travel <del rend="none" hand="h1"/> your Pa would be better Satisfied if Ma
                    was here to <orig reg="wait">wate</orig> on him. <pb n="2"/> I have <orig
                        reg="been">bin</orig> well my Self I never <orig reg="enjoyed"
                    >injoyed</orig> better health in my life I hope you are all well at home Diana
                    &amp; all are well</p>

                <p>
                    <del rend="none" hand="h1"/>
                </p>

                <p>The Dr <orig reg="don't">dont</orig> think your Pa is in any Danger he Says the
                    ride from Washington was too <orig reg="great">greate</orig> under taken <del
                        hand="h1">for</del> for him he was too <del hand="h1">weake</del>
                    <orig reg="weak">wek</orig> to travel if he had of Sayed over in <del hand="h1"
                        >Washn</del> Washington he would not have have this <orig reg="spell"
                    >Spel</orig></p>

                <p>I think <del rend="none" hand="h1"/> your Pa will be <orig reg="able">abel</orig> to Make the
                    trip home by Thursday if not Sooner. I am Sorry Ma did not get the Telegram in
                    time to come <orig reg="today">to Day.</orig></p>

                <p>love to all</p>

                <p>I Send love &amp; Kiss to you I have thought of you ever Day Since I have
                        <orig reg="been">bin</orig>
                    <orig reg="away">a way</orig> good bye. Write Soon to me.</p>

                <closer>
                    <salute>Your afect Husband</salute>
                    <signed>D H Evans</signed>
                </closer>
            </div1>
        </body>
    </text>
